prompts.outline_user:
Please create a complete outline for a {genre} novel titled «{title}».

Character Setting: {character_setting}

World Setting: {world_setting}

Core Plot: {plot_idea}

Style Requirements: {style_desc}

{custom_prompt}Requirements:
1. MUST have EXACTLY {total_chapters} chapters, no more, no less. MUST LIST EVERY SINGLE CHAPTER IN DETAIL.
2. Each chapter MUST start on a new line with strict format: Chapter X: Chapter Title - Brief plot description (50-100 words)
3. ABSOLUTELY NO grouping chapters together (do NOT write Chapter 1-5).
4. DO NOT USE group headings (like Volume 1, Arc 1, Part 1) to group chapters. List them flatly from top to bottom.
5. Coherent plot with beginning - development - climax - ending, reasonable character development.
6. Output ONLY the outline list, no comments or extra explanations.

prompts.chapter_user:
Write chapter {chapter_num} for the novel 《{novel_title}》.

Chapter Title: {chapter_title}
Chapter Plan: {chapter_desc}

Characters: {character_setting}
World: {world_setting}
Plot Idea: {plot_idea}

Style: {style_desc}

Requirements:
1. Around {target_words} words
2. Stick strictly to the chapter plan
3. Dialogues must be natural and fit character profiles
4. Leave a hook or suspense at the end
5. 'Show, don't tell' principle for emotions
6. Balance action, dialog, and thoughts
7. ONLY OUTPUT the actual story text, no titles or meta-commentary{continuity_prompt}{context_prompt}

