prompts.suggest_world_user:
Design a world setting (150-200 words).

Title Concept: {title}
Genre: {genre}

Output details of rules, powers, history, and social structures. Just the content.

prompts.suggest_plot_user:
Design the core main plot (200-250 words).

Title: {title}
Genre: {genre}
Characters: {character_setting}
World: {world_setting}

Include a hook, mid-point twist, and climax. Just output the plot.

prompts.continue_user:
Continue the next chapter of 《{novel_title}》.

[Base Lore]
Char: {character_setting}
World: {world_setting}
Plot: {plot_idea}

[Style]
{style_desc}

[Recent Text](~1500 words)
{previous_content}

[Rules]
1. Continue naturally
2. Match previous tone, dialogue, state
3. ~{target_words} words
4. DO NOT repeat
5. ONLY actual text, no titles.

